quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  10,53,WE JESTENBI’UNEKE ‘EHEKKUN HUWE KUL ‘I WE RABBI ‘INNEHU LEHEKKUN WE MA ‘ENTUM BIMU’XHIZINE
  10,54,WE LEW ‘ENNE LIKULLI NEFSIN DHELEMET MA FIL-’ERDI LAFTEDET BIHI WE ‘ESERRU EN-NEDAMETE LEMMA RE’EWL-’ADHABE WE KUDIJE BEJNEHUM BIL-KISTI WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  10,55,‘ELA ‘INNE LILLAHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘ELA ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  10,56,HUWE JUHJI WE JUMITU WE ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  10,57,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU KAD XHA’ETKUM MEW’IDHETUN MIN RABBIKUM WE SHIFA’UN LIMA FI ES-SUDURI WE HUDEN WE REHMETUN LILMU’UMININE
  10,58,KUL BIFEDLI ELLAHI WE BIREHMETIHI FEBIDHALIKE FELJEFREHU HUWE HAJRUN MIMMA JEXHMA’UNE
  10,59,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU LEKUM MIN RIZKIN FEXHE’ALTUM MINHU HERAMÆN WE HELALÆN KUL ‘ALLLEHU ‘EDHINE LEKUM ‘EM ‘ALA ELLAHI TEFTERUNE
  10,60,WE MA DHENNUL-LEDHINE JEFTERUNE ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEDHU FEDLIN ‘ALA EN-NASI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JESHKURUNE
  10,61,WE MA TEKUNU FI SHE’NIN WE MA TETLU MINHU MIN KUR’ANIN WE LA TA’MELUNE MIN ‘AMELIN ‘ILLA KUNNA ‘ALEJKUM SHUHUDÆN ‘IDH TUFIDUNE FIHI WE MA JA’ZUBU ‘AN RABBIKE MIN MITHKALI DHERRETIN FIL-’ERDI WE LA FI ES-SEMA’I WE LA ‘ESGARE MIN DHALIKE WE LA ‘EKBERE ‘ILLA
  10,62,‘ELA ‘INNE ‘EWLIJA’EL-LAHI LA HAWFUN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  10,63,EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE KANU JETTEKUNE
  10,64,LEHUMUL-BUSHRA FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE FIL-’AHIRETI LA TEBDILE LIKELIMATI ELLAHI DHALIKE HUWEL-FEWZUL-’ADHIMU
  10,65,WE LA JEHZUNKE KAWLUHUM ‘INNEL-’IZZETE LILLAHI XHEMI’ÆN HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  10,66,‘ELA ‘INNE LILLAHI MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MEN FIL-’ERDI WE MA JETTEBI’UL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI SHUREKA’E ‘IN JETTEBI’UNE ‘ILLA EDH-DHENNE WE ‘IN HUM ‘ILLA JEHRUSUNE
  10,67,HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-LEJLE LITESKUNU FIHI WE EN-NEHARE MUBSIRÆN ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JESMA’UNE
  10,68,KALU ETTEHADHEL-LAHU WELEDÆN SUBHANEHU HUWEL-GANIJU LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI ‘IN ‘INDEKUM MIN SULTANIN BIHEDHA ‘ETEKULUNE ‘ALA ELLAHI MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  10,69,KUL ‘INNEL-LEDHINE JEFTERUNE ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE LA JUFLIHUNE
  10,70,META’UN FI ED-DUNJA THUMME ‘ILEJNA MERXHI’UHUM THUMME NUDHIKUHUMUL-’ADHABE ESH-SHEDIDE BIMA KANU JEKFURUNE